            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "STTA",
                "ACTIV",
                "EXTB",
                "GSPEC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " 2 stacks were irradiated with",
                "proton beam of 16 MeV in Faraday-cup type holder.",
                "Measurements started after 7 week and 18 weeks after",
                "EOB. The beam intensities obtained via  charge",
                "collection were corrected with the data from the",
                "monitor reaction. The energy degradation was",
                "initially determined by calculation using  the",
                "SRIM2010 web based calculation tool and",
                "corrected on the basis of the measured monitor",
                "reaction excitation function. The nuclear data",
                "were taken from the NUDAT2 database. Correction for",
                "led X-rays induced in the detector shielding was made."
              ]
            }
          ],
